high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the mug in the sink.
Walk ahead and veer left to the fridge.
Place the mug on the bottom shelf. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Place the mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the white coffee cup that is in the sink.
With the coffee cup in hand turn and go the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Set the coffee cup on the middle of the top shelf.  Shut the fridge.  Open the fridge and grab the coffee cup on thee top shelf.
Turn and go to the microwave with the coffee cup in hand.
Open the microwave and place the coffee mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup in fridge and  in microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink on your left.
Grab a cup from the sink.
Walk to the fridge on your right.
Place the cup in the fridge, then take it out.
Walk to the microwave next to the fridge.
Put the cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup to microwave it.
